{"type": "article", "id": 44649, "title": "卡戴珊扮演杰奎琳，以及，摇滚名人堂来到东京出展 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-08-30T03:20:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 26148, "name": "摇滚名人堂"}, {"id": 12570, "name": "拍立得"}, {"id": 37054, "name": "Côte&Ciel"}, {"id": 6117, "name": "卡戴珊"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170830102020zVbIsPreqNS58vRE.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://sc.stock.cnfol.com/ggzixun/20170829/25247859.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>森马发布上半年财报，儿童服饰板块收入超 22 亿元</strong></a> | 今年上半年，森马服饰实现营收 44.33 亿元，同比增长了 14.28％，实现营业利润 7.15 亿元。其中，儿童服饰营收为 22.46 亿元，占比 50.68%，同比增长了 24.97%。</p><p><a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/hkstock/ggscyd/2017-08-29/doc-ifykiqfe2663865.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>达芙妮中期亏损扩大 28％，至 2.09 亿港元</strong></a> | 截止至 6 月 30 日的上半年，达芙妮国际营业额大跌 19.65%，至 27.33 亿港元，亏损扩大 28%，至 2.09 亿港元。报告期内 ，达芙妮上半年门店数净减少 306 家，关闭了 47 家加盟店和 259 家直营店，平均每月关店 55 家。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/j-jill-posts-q2-results-shares-decline-softer-guidance-retail-apparel-10967721/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国服饰品牌 J.Jill 第二季度净利润大涨 47.2% </strong></a>| 截止至 7 月 29 日的三个月内，J.Jill 销售额同比上涨 9.9% 至 1.81 亿美元，净利润则大涨了 47.2％，至 1200 万美元。该集团称，将继续通过改善产品分类和门店购物体验等方式来促进业绩进一步增长。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/462859\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本星巴克与英国 Cath Kidson 品牌合作</a>，将从 9 月 4 日起发售包括保温杯、马克杯和明信片系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102154fr0lOL4wXa3FMUNy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102159Axjrp8wkYQHuGvW5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665354\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>金·卡戴珊带着小西北，扮成美国国民偶像杰奎琳·肯尼迪的样子出现在<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/news/kim-kardashian-steven-klein-interview-magazine-fashion-280717\" rel=\"nofollow\">《Interview Magazine》九月刊</a>中，杂志称她是“美国新第一夫人”。但这事儿引起了不小的争议，很多人觉得杰奎琳是不能被取代的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102131ub0X7PZTkKhBRoEN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301021320FGvxUX6Md1hKHit.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301021339fg5EThrBqvubSJI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102133Xu2Leb97JUK3ANYs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102133yoG1OCsvTdzASqIt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102134FT9kZrAB6lmNqQDs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102134nxQvlySdNAXuDYf1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102134yCiAmv5oRruwePIL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102139gGlJmFPk8YC3hLjW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102139HXh2QJB9mCGnFyP0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.291436\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/cote-ciel-2017-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">法国箱包品牌 Côte&amp;Ciel 发布 2017 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>。新系列在一贯的黑色调中加入了迷彩配色，以及高级牛皮等特殊面料，售价在 225 至 860 美元之间。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102325thLYODwRsQBbSoXu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301023112rWZMnEQbay75hxU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102312PXtyoUZg6BVJaTcH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102311Mj3UhV1PTrin7euL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102312OzMJYDnx1g73QEsA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301023120FTelE4durKU3zQO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102312b7X5MvzwhqJdeWtN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102314MK7OujXmIZStnoAk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301023163G9bDynfxjmMXTQz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102316jt1Vi8b7z6g5cW3K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102316Sg9rW46OdulhLNnD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102317jZ3ceNGBnwYxU6mW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102317awTRv5DK9BcMAFqS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102319WdsUqOwPBeJlfKEI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102320dki7Eyn6wzjv43Tr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102320RgDhq9EU4cFb05CB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102319tHSzdeAsnp3mrLKQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/8/lomography-lomoinstant-square-kickstarter\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lomography 计划推出 Lomo’Instant Square 方形拍立得相机</a>，这款相机是全球首部全胶片设计、使用 Instax Square 方形相纸的拍立得相机，折叠式设计令其十分便携。目前，这款相机正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lomography/the-lomoinstant-square-camera#\" rel=\"nofollow\"> kickstarter </a>上进行众筹，9 月 29 日截止。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102413gfLovNSUw2bRxtkr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102413IqWuxXKPzMYe5JR3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102417G6ZflSuzXtTEaLxJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102417x6NJILuRfVFMlCjD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>位于美国俄亥俄州克利夫兰的摇滚名人堂博物馆首次出展海外。9 月 23 日，<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-08-29/rockandroll-halloffame/\" rel=\"nofollow\">摇滚名人堂日本馆</a>将于东京有乐町开幕，展馆面积约为 600 平方米，届时将会展出摇滚明星的舞台服装、写真、爱用品等物品，<a href=\"http://rrhfj.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官网</a>购票渠道现已开启。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201708301024487kmEXvFIA8QRtSNf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102445fEinNyeDAaT1UGtd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102445yIYuVmPXZ6FDikvt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170830102445JHg6oOKFVEywPfNm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/news/kim-kardashian-steven-klein-interview-magazine-fashion-280717\" rel=\"nofollow\">itsnicethat</a></p>"}